channel.name: Mediso DICOM Transformer
channel.description: This channels remaps the AccessionNumber tag on images from Mediso gammacameras, correcting an error where the AccessionNumber tag is blank.

step.name: Header
step.script: var mapping;try { mapping = tmp=msg; }catch (e) { logger.error(e); mapping = '';}channelMap.put('Header', validate( mapping , '', new Array()));

step.name: AccNo
step.script: var mapping;try { mapping = tmp['tag00080050']=msg['tag00200010'].toString(); }catch (e) { logger.error(e); mapping = '';}channelMap.put('AccNo', validate( mapping , '', new Array()));

step.name: AccNoLength
step.script: var mapping;try { mapping = tmp['tag00080050']['@len']=msg['tag00200010']['@len'].toString(); }catch (e) { logger.error(e); mapping = '';}channelMap.put('AccNoLength', validate( mapping , '', new Array()));

channel.preprocessingScript: // Modify the message variable below to pre process data return message;
